(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 350.52 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 29f58358-d9ab-46e1-a37c-b12fbb650f12))
(text "M.2 E-key PCIe lane follows the existing Mu-host-to-socket naming convention used by the NVMe M-key slot." (at 20.32 358.14 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 9ad47368-512a-4cb9-8fa5-7e883be0e9bf))
(text "USB2_P1 is reserved for the E-key Bluetooth/USB function; HSIO1 is reserved for the E-key PCIe lane." (at 20.32 365.76 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d6e1c93a-9793-4c3b-b82a-a1aac06827dd))
(text "Target radio is an Intel AX210-class M.2 2230 Key-E module: Wi-Fi over PCIe, Bluetooth over USB." (at 20.32 373.38 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 4de12d89-89cc-4d48-9914-c0411bdd159a))
(text "OLED headers are SSD1306 I2C: GND, 3V3, SCL, SDA, RES, SA0. Use 3.3V OLED modules only." (at 20.32 381 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 34db7a20-7bf3-4084-8f17-e041ce8096c0))
(text "MAX-M10S uses EC UART here. VIO_SEL, SAFEBOOT_N, SDA/SCL, VCC_RF, and LNA_EN are NC." (at 20.32 388.62 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid de1153d1-a57d-46bc-8b6c-cda9fefda825))
(text "OLED A defaults to 0x3C; OLED B defaults to 0x3D. Do not run both at the same address." (at 20.32 396.24 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 870d1108-2243-41a4-98d9-2863674f5a6b))
(text "GNSS RF layout: place U.FL near board edge, route RF_IN as 50 ohm, and keep it away from Wi-Fi antennas/noisy bucks." (at 20.32 403.86 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 8a793ee1-9e1c-447a-a1e3-03786089c417))
(text "Avoid CNVio/CNVio2-only E-key modules unless LattePanda Mu support is explicitly verified." (at 20.32 411.48 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 3793079a-d2f4-4731-9bdf-d72f4090fe1d))
(text "R195/L40/C176/C177 are DNP active-GNSS-antenna bias options; leave open for passive antennas." (at 20.32 419.1 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid b0cadf97-d717-4b39-aab9-f3bf3d9f86fd))
(text "SUSCLK, SDIO, PCM/I2S, UIM, and vendor-defined E-key pins remain NC for the AX210-class module target." (at 20.32 426.72 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid daf6c021-24e3-4c95-98b0-1d86796ff9d6))
